cs481.postag
Class POSTag

java.lang.Object
  cs481.postag.POSTag

public class POSTag
extends java.lang.Object

Uses Hidden Markov Model to determine the part of speech tags. 

 Typical use:
 POSTag pt = new POSTag();
 pt.train(training);
 pt.tag(testing);
Run from the commandline.

Author:
Sterling Stuart Stein
